# AI Assistant Specification

## 1. Core Functionality

### 1.1. Design Assistant
- **Component Generation**
  - Generate UI components from text descriptions
  - Suggest component improvements
  - Provide responsive design options
  - Create component variations

- **Layout Optimization**
  - Suggest layout improvements
  - Optimize component placement
  - Ensure responsive behavior
  - Maintain design consistency

- **UX Suggestions**
  - Best practices recommendations
  - Accessibility improvements
  - User flow optimization
  - Interactive element placement

### 1.2. Backend Assistant
- **API Development**
  - Generate API endpoints
  - Suggest API structure
  - Create API documentation
  - Optimize API performance

- **Database Design**
  - Schema suggestions
  - Relationship optimization
  - Index recommendations
  - Performance improvements

## 2. Technical Requirements

### 2.1. AI Integration
- Integration with modern LLMs
- Context-aware responses
- Real-time suggestions
- Response caching system

### 2.2. Performance
- Response time < 3 seconds
- Efficient resource usage
- Scalable architecture
- Optimized token usage

### 2.3. User Interface
- Intuitive suggestion display
- Non-intrusive assistance
- Clear feedback system
- Easy interaction methods

## 3. Implementation Details

### 3.1. AI Model Requirements
- Context window: 16K tokens minimum
- Support for code generation
- Understanding of no-code concepts
- Multi-turn conversation capability

### 3.2. Integration Points
- Visual editor integration
- Workflow builder integration
- Database designer integration
- API builder integration

## 4. Security Considerations
- Secure API communication
- Data privacy protection
- Code validation
- Access control

## 5. Success Metrics
- Suggestion accuracy > 70%
- User acceptance rate > 60%
- Performance within limits
- Positive user feedback
